com.xhive.dom.xlink.interfaces
Interface XhiveLinkBehaviourIf

All Known Subinterfaces:
XhiveArcIf, XhiveSimpleLinkIf
public interface XhiveLinkBehaviourIf

Represents XLink behaviour. Link behavour is defined by the XLink namespace attributes show and actuate.

Link classes XhiveSimpleLinkIf and XhiveArcIf extend this interface.

(c) X-Hive Corporation B.V. (www.x-hive.com)
